    "It does not operate as a black box, simply churning out solutions to ambiguous design problems.",
    "Instead, it actively involves designers at every stage, allowing them to review the output and make revisions as needed.",
    "Consequently, designers gain a deeper understanding of the situation.",
    "This fosters a high level of interaction between the designer and the LLM.",
    "However, this study did not explore the impact of designer interaction with the LLM on design projects."
